<p>Perplexity referral traffic appears in GA4 under <strong>Acquisition &gt; Traffic Acquisition</strong>. Filter by source/medium containing "perplexity."</p>
<p>The referral URL pattern is:</p>
<pre><code>perplexity.ai / referral
</code></pre>
<p>Create a custom segment for Perplexity traffic to track page views, session duration, and conversions from this channel separately.</p>
<h3>Server Log Analysis</h3>
<p>Check your server logs for PerplexityBot crawl activity. Increasing crawl frequency is a leading indicator. If PerplexityBot crawls your pages more often, your content is entering its retrieval pipeline.</p>
<h3>Manual Citation Checks</h3>
<p>Search your target queries on Perplexity weekly. Document which of your pages appear as citations. Track citation count, position, and the specific claims your page supports. Our guide on <a href="/blog/track-ai-search-visibility/">tracking AI search visibility</a> covers the full measurement framework.</p>
